screen_name: I tested positive for Covid-19 on 4/5.  At that time I had only experienced a loss of smell.  I remained "A" symptomatic the entire time and spent 14 days in isolation.  I am grateful that I was never sick but why am I wearing a mask now?  Why can't I go anywhere I want? #COVID19
